layerGroup.name: bathymetry_AMP_ME_depthzones
layerGroup.title: Bathymetry of Australian Marine Parks (AMPs) - styled by Parks Australia ME depth zone
layerGroup.abstractTxt:
Multibeam bathymetry data complied from various sources and compiled into a single Geotiff per Australian Marine Park (AMP). Each AMP Geotiff is gridded to the equivalent of the finest resolution of data available in that region and represents a multi-resolution mosaic. Styling is according to the depth zones of the Parks Australia Management Effectiveness (ME) language. [NVCL, MERI]
This layer group comprises of bathymetry mosaics overlaid on derived hillshade, clipped to the boundaries of Australian Marine Parks (2023).
The bathymetry data is current as of 2024.
